{"tid":2280563,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚晚 The 5B Private Corner","createTime":"2020-11-10T14:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T08:58:19.000Z","uid":310853,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f07d6f1b108434427f6aaaa2f9ea51a5eff67649","tid":2280563,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"今日個朋友生日 就佢過咗荃灣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKaraaR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKaraaR.png&h=ecf07260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依碟係黑毛豬嚟<br />\n好少食過百蚊嘅豬<br />\n食落都幾嫩滑 都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3owmh3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3owmh3.png&h=a54f980b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MB2sYC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MB2sYC.png&h=4955951b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩碟都係牛肩肉嚟<br />\n雖然唔知點解唔同樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但味道都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7e1f00f03028b7f740a2f14c2ca08c0ee0add7","tid":2280563,"uid":326470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"輪住生日餐可以食足成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f314dfd134956fbb565919e25fe11a1a73a0c3a","tid":2280563,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba4bffc4b173c52a653ef5f074f30c5738a2ca9","tid":2280563,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f7e1f00f03028b7f740a2f14c2ca08c0ee0add7","tid":2280563,"uid":326470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"